               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17850406-29-cd136" type="crimeDate">6th day of March</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17850406-29-off135 t17850406-29-cd136"></join> last, one pair of cloth breeches, value 2 s. a cloth waistcoat, value 3 s. a coat, value 10 s. a pair of silk breeches, value 2 s. a silk waistcoat, value 2 s. a woollen jacket, value 1 s. a linen shirt, value 1 s. a silver watch, value 30 s. the property of 
                     
                        <persName id="t17850406-29-victim364" type="victimName">
